  <description>
    <p>Lemonade is an open-source Nintendo 3DS emulator/debugger "fork" written in C++. It is written with portability in mind, with builds actively maintained for Windows, Linux and macOS.</p>
    <p>Lemonade plans to add new features/enhacments on top of the __base__ emulator which was taken down by their team</p>
